{"tid":1541910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Do you hear the people sing 世界民主國家合唱好想有香港份","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T17:02:46.000Z","uid":217242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"558052e52baa7aff23de0bde290c479127f1cd8c","tid":1541910,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望香港有朝一日都可以<br />\n同班民主國家一齊合唱</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[size=5]<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>如果每次係前線播或者一齊唱</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一定程度上可以振奮軍心</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我認為<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>比<span style=\"color: gold;\">烏</span>克<span style=\"color: blue;\">蘭</span><br />\n少咗一份身份自我認同同埋國歌 <br />\n<br />\n我覺得如果有一首歌可以connect到前線同幕後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對呢場運動/革命都非常有幫助<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地除咗獅子山下同海闊天空<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有無其他激昂歌可以帶動香港人情緒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AdQpQgYHc4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAdQpQgYHc4w&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=6dff3ed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AdQpQgYHc4w</a> <br />\n1:46開始唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/47E2tfK5QAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F47E2tfK5QAg&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=9637719a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/47E2tfK5QAg</a><br />\n原版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d3f6a1d4ad4708101ae03f71f41a0d68f82c11","tid":1541910,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18514bb69f8ec204e9349eca115b6ea7851defa0","tid":1541910,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b1998b20aad4416fd4f979337aa39df21da9c48","tid":1541910,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbcff2ed241f39702ff278d5c5c83ecc79a69d7","tid":1541910,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a86c61a4c92124bf2777b9e16e30e74c08119e1","tid":1541910,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18514bb69f8ec204e9349eca115b6ea7851defa0","tid":1541910,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"<span st